# Ad-hoc predictions CSVs (large, scratch) -- same relative path locally and on the cluster,
# so nothing lands loose in the repo root. Worth-keeping ones get copied into predictions/ and
# committed deliberately -- see README. Slurm .out logs go to logs/ instead, which IS
# committed (small, and $WORK has no backup guarantee).
/runs/*
!/runs/.gitkeep

# Trained LoRA adapters (scripts/train_lora.py output) -- large, same reasoning as /runs/ above.
/adapters/*
!/adapters/.gitkeep